org: cassriorp28
# "app" enables Serverless Framework Dashboard features and sharing them with other Services.
app: serveless-agendamentos
# "service" is the name of this project. This will also be added to your AWS resource names.
service: serveless-agendamentos

plugins:
  - serverless-offline

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs20.x
  stage: dev
  region: us-east-1
  memorySize: 128
  timeout: 3

functions:
  getAgendas:
    handler: src/agenda/controller/AgendaController.buscarAgendas
    description: "Busca as agendas de medicos"
    events:
      - httpApi:
          path: /agendas
          method: get
  postAgendamento:
    handler: src/agendamento/controller/AgendamentoController.marcarAgendamento
    events:
      - httpApi:
          path: /agendamento
          method: post
